    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey guys! I\u2019m selling my car and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one! It\u2019s perfect for commuting or weekend trips, and I\u2019m sure the next owner is going to love it just as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 28900.0,
