    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a perfect blend of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though minor road chips consistent with careful use are visible upon close inspection. Inside, the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronics, including the dual-zone climate control and infotainment system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is in great health, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and full synthetic oil service just last month. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives straight and true, with a quiet cabin and smooth gear transitions. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that has been smoke-free and garage-kept.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
