      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver who values both mechanical integrity and refined presentation. Meticulously maintained and subject to a rigorous multi-point inspection, the automobile delivers a consistent and sophisticated driving experience. It stands as a testament to diligent ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and long-term value for those who demand excellence in their daily commute.",
      "price": 34500.0,
