    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It looks great and runs smoothly\u2014I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive. Can't wait to hear from you!",
      "price": 29500.0,
