    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring six individual throttle bodies and a factory-rated 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a variable M-differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Crucially, the Achilles' heels of this chassis have been addressed: the VANOS system has been overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced for enhanced torsional rigidity. The suspension features upgraded Bilstein dampers, maintaining precise turn-in and dampening characteristics. While the aesthetics reflect its status as an enjoyed enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical vitals\u2014including valve clearances and rod bearing health\u2014are robust. A visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning pilot.",
